Typedef Documentation

typedef enum SOC_ModuleId_e SOC_ModuleId

Enumeration for system peripheral module id.

The enumeration defines the system peripheral module id to be used to configure clock, memory initialization etc.

typedef enum SOC_SecureFirewallModule_e SOC_SecureFirewallModule

SOC Secure device firewall capable modules.

The bitmap enum defines the modules that can have firewall enabled/disabled on a secure device
